OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778778356
OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering model after
OL,4,Cattempting to flee the country
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering a 37-year-old model and DJ
OL,8,Fin Rossendale.
OL,10,FBhekisani Matabiswana attacked model
OL,11,FLuke Harden on 1 November 2025 as he
OL,12,Fleft a Halloween party, before he
OL,13,Fattempted to flee the country.
OL,15,FLuke was booked to DJ at the party at
OL,16,Fa working men's club in Huttock End
OL,17,FLane in Stacksteads that Matabiswana
OL,18,Fwas attending.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
