FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778778356
OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering model after
OL,4,Cattempting to flee the country
OL,6,FBoth men left seperately, but CCTV
OL,7,Ffootage captured Matabiswana and his
OL,8,Fgroup ahead of Luke as they walked
OL,9,Fthrough the area.
OL,11,FShortly after, Matabiswana and a woman
OL,12,Fseparated from their friends and
OL,13,Fencountered Luke on Newchurch Road.
OL,15,FIt was there that Matabiswana launched
OL,16,Fthe assault on Luke, punching him and
OL,17,Fthen kicking or stamping on him as he
OL,18,Flay defenceless on the ground. Luke
OL,19,Fhad no defensive wounds, and there was
OL,20,Fno evidence to suggest he was the
OL,21,Faggressor, the court heard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778778356
OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering model after
OL,4,Cattempting to flee the country
OL,6,FMatabiswana then used Luke's phone to
OL,7,Fcall his friends and family, telling
OL,8,Fthem their loved one was on the floor,
OL,9,Fbut did not call for an ambulance or
OL,10,Foffer first aid.
OL,12,FA member of the public eventually
OL,13,Ftried to help Luke and called
OL,14,Femergency services.
OL,16,FParamedics arrived but could not save
OL,17,FLuke, who was pronounced dead at the
OL,18,Fscene.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778778356
OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering model after
OL,4,Cattempting to flee the country
OL,6,FHe suffered severe head and neck
OL,7,Finjuries, including brain swelling,
OL,8,Fbroken facial bones, and bruising.
OL,10,FIt was later established that he died
OL,11,Fas a result of blunt force trauma to
OL,12,Fthe head and neck following an assault.
OL,14,FMatabiswana lied to paramedics and
OL,15,Fpolice, claiming that Luke had simply
OL,16,Ffallen, and later tried to flee the
OL,17,FUK, booking a flight to South Africa.
OL,19,FHe was arrested at Manchester Airport
OL,20,Fthe following day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
