FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778778356
OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering model after
OL,4,Cattempting to flee the country
OL,6,FDuring the investigation, Matabiswana
OL,7,Fgave conflicting accounts to police
OL,8,Fand via text messages, including
OL,9,Fclaims of self-defence, which were
OL,10,Frejected by the jury.
OL,12,FHe showed no remorse, and police said
OL,13,Fhe made several attempts to evade
OL,14,Fjustice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
