PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778778356
OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering model after
OL,4,Cattempting to flee the country
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Pete MacDonald
OL,7,Fsaid: "Following a brief encounter
OL,8,Fwith his victim, Matabiswana engaged
OL,9,Fin a frenzied and cowardly attack `
OL,10,Fcontinuing to attack Luke whilst he
OL,11,Flay defenceless on the floor...
OL,12,FThroughout this case, Matabiswana has
OL,13,Fshown no remorse, making several
OL,14,Fefforts to evade justice."
OL,16,FMatabiswana will be sentenced at
OL,17,FPreston Crown Court on Monday 18 May.
OL,26,@oD@GOUvD@ZO]
